# Flutter Feature Development вҖ” Full Workflow

## вҡ пёҸ MCP Critical Rules

### Figma MCP:
- Raw numbers (16, 20) вҶ’ convert to `AppSize`/`AppPadding`/`AppCircular`
- **Colors вҶ’ read `color_manager.dart` FIRST, reuse existing AppColors by purpose** (e.g. dark text вҶ’ `AppColors.primary`, grey text вҶ’ `AppColors.hintText`, light bg вҶ’ `AppColors.fill`). Only add truly new colors with **generic names** вҖ” NEVER screen-prefixed (`loginPrimary` вқҢ)
- **Font sizes вҶ’ Figma вүӨ13sp keep as-is, Figma 14-18sp reduce by 1вҖ“2sp, Figma вүҘ20sp reduce by 2sp** (Figma 12 вҶ’ `.s12`, Figma 16 вҶ’ `.s14`, Figma 22 вҶ’ `.s20`)
- **Screen-level body padding > 12px вҶ’ reduce by 2вҖ“4px** (Figma 16 вҶ’ 12 or 14, Figma 20 вҶ’ 16). вүӨ 12px вҶ’ keep as-is.
- **RTL Section Verification** вҖ” Figma MCP sometimes returns sections mirrored. ALWAYS cross-check with the visual screenshot. Verify: Arabic text starts from RIGHT, horizontal lists/filters start from RIGHT, card images match Figma visual position. Trust screenshot over raw MCP data.
- **Icon background check** вҖ” some AppAssets icons already include their background. Check before wrapping in Container. If icon has built-in bg вҶ’ use directly. If transparent вҶ’ add Container bg.
- App is RTL вҖ” read positions from Figma AS-IS, never mirror
- No `Directionality` widget on layouts (exception: wrapping a single Text widget to fix mirrored text inside complex components like Slider/DropdownButton)
- No `Icons.*` from Material вҖ” use `AppAssets` only

### Postman MCP:
- Every Entity needs `factory initial()` вҖ” mandatory
- Every `fromJson` field needs `?? defaultValue` or nullable
- One cubit per endpoint вҖ” never merge
- Check response fully for pagination before starting

### RTL вҖ” Mandatory Check on EVERY Screen:
- `CrossAxisAlignment.start` вҶ’ physical RIGHT (use for Arabic text alignment) вң…
- `CrossAxisAlignment.end` вҶ’ physical LEFT вң…
- `AlignmentDirectional.centerStart` вҶ’ physical RIGHT вң…
- `PositionedDirectional(start:)` вҶ’ physical RIGHT вң…
- `PositionedDirectional(end:)` вҶ’ physical LEFT вң…
- Row: first child вҶ’ physical RIGHT, last child вҶ’ physical LEFT
- Never: `Positioned(left/right:)`, `Align(Alignment.centerLeft/Right)`, `EdgeInsets.only(left/right:)`, `TextAlign.left`

