## PHASE 2 вҖ” Figma Analysis

### Read ALL screens for the feature:
1. Main screen (default state)
2. Empty state
3. Loading/skeleton state
4. Error state
5. All modals & bottom sheets
6. Success/failure states
7. Pagination load-more state (if applicable)

### For every Figma value:
```
Color hex вҶ’ match AppColors вҶ’ add if not found
Number px вҶ’ match AppSize/AppPadding/AppMargin вҶ’ add if not found
Font size вҶ’ match FontSizeManager вҶ’ add if not found
Icon вҶ’ match AppAssets вҶ’ add if not found
```

